Package: pregnancy
Title: Calculate and Track Dates and Medications During Pregnancy
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(
        given = "Ella",
        family = "Kaye",
        role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
        email = "ella.kaye@gmail.com",
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7300-3718")
    )
Description: Provides functionality for calculating pregnancy-related dates and 
    tracking medications during pregnancy and fertility treatment. Calculates 
    due dates from various starting points including last menstrual period and 
    IVF transfer dates, determines pregnancy progress on any given date, and 
    identifies when specific pregnancy weeks are reached. Also calculates 
    optimal pregnancy test dates based on cycle timing and test sensitivity. 
    Includes medication tracking capabilities for individuals undergoing 
    fertility treatment or during pregnancy, allowing users to monitor remaining 
    doses and quantities needed over specified time periods. Designed for those 
    tracking their own pregnancies or supporting partners through the process, 
    making use of options to personalise output messages.
